# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# COMMONS — environment variables (example)
# Copy to ".env" for local development. NEVER commit a real ".env".
#
# Only ONE variable is needed to run the app today. On Google AI Studio /
# Cloud Run, GEMINI_API_KEY is injected automatically from your account, so
# you do not set it there. Additional variables will be added in later steps
# as those features are built (and documented here when they are real).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Gemini API key (server-side only — never prefix with VITE_).
# Local dev: paste your key here. On AI Studio: injected automatically.
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Port the server listens on. Cloud Run / AI Studio set this automatically.
PORT=3000
